  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "CZ EVO 3 A1 \"蝎式\" 9x19毫米冲锋枪",
      "en": "CZ Scorpion EVO 3 A1 9x19 submachine gun"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "EVO 3",
      "en": "EVO 3"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "CZ EVO 3 \"蝎式\"是由捷克乌赫尔斯基布罗德兵工厂生产的9毫米卡宾枪，其可选射击模式的冲锋枪版本代号为A1型，半自动版本代号为S1型。EVO 3的命名表明该枪械是继vz.61蝎式冲锋枪（两者无机械关联）之后，CZ公司第三代小型冲锋枪系列产品。",
      "en": "The CZ Scorpion EVO 3 is a 9mm carbine manufactured by Česká zbrojovka Uherský Brod, the select-fire submachine gun variant is designated A1, and the semi-automatic variant is designated S1. The EVO 3 designation denotes that the firearm is a third generation of CZ's line of small submachine guns started by the Škorpion vz. 61, which is mechanically unrelated."
    },
